Recently I learned that my step-dad has not only played but BEATEN Final Fantasy 6. Although he referred to it as Final Fantasy 3. I think I blew his mind when I explained the 3 was actually 6.[/bq]

@YOUR ENTIRE FAMILY IS FREAKING COOL AND AWESOME@
